title: DogWorld 3D: My Puppy v1.1.83
description:
The sweetest animal playing app "DogWorld 3D: My Puppy" for all big and small children who always dream of having a dog. The cute little Dalmatian baby puppy is waiting for you to play with him. This dog is a true companion: you can take him anywhere and everywhere with you.

FEATURES
- The animal playing app for big and small dog lovers
- Your low-maintenance, virtual pet to play with and take care of
- Cool 3D graphics
- Collect stars to save for surprises
- Frequent updates and cool upgrades

YOUR VIRTUAL DOG FOR PLAYING, PETTING AND CUDDLING

Your puppy reacts to touches on the touchscreen - this is how you can spoil him all around. He's always happy when you visit him because he's a cuddly and playful dog, who simply puts everyone in a good mood. The more you play with him the more surprises wait for you: in every new level you'll receive a gift box with many accessories for your dog plus treats and toys that every puppy loves.

THIS PUPPY LOVES DANCING AND DRESSING UP

In this animal playing game you can do more than just pet and wash your pet. You have your own room where you can dress him up and photograph him. Your puppy loves posing for the camera. There are always new upgrades for the costume box so that it's never boring. In an additional room your Dalmatian shows you his lumbering dance moves to diverse songs that you can select.

What's in this version:
Ruff, a new room is available! It's off to the cellar and onto the trampoline. Teach the little Dalmatian the wildest tricks! More surprises are coming soon!
